  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657130/extras/4d00f9393f2069099167d707d73302f0.poster.avif?t=1700134043\" width=614 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657130/extras/4d00f9393f2069099167d707d73302f0.webm?t=1700134043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657130/extras/4d00f9393f2069099167d707d73302f0.mp4?t=1700134043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Wormswarm is an experimental platformer about jumping on abstract wriggling worms while scoring points. The game is based on a simple concept - the ground under your feet is constantly moving. Your goal is to score as many points as possible, dodge all the dangerous red worms and not fall into the abyss...<br>The huge number of moving objects forces you to quickly find the best routes and show miracles of reaction to get to the top of the leaderboard!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657130/extras/4d00f9393f2069099167d707d73302f0.poster.avif?t=1700134043\" width=614 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657130/extras/4d00f9393f2069099167d707d73302f0.webm?t=1700134043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657130/extras/4d00f9393f2069099167d707d73302f0.mp4?t=1700134043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Wormswarm is an experimental platformer about jumping on abstract wriggling worms while scoring points. The game is based on a simple concept - the ground under your feet is constantly moving. Your goal is to score as many points as possible, dodge all the dangerous red worms and not fall into the abyss...<br>The huge number of moving objects forces you to quickly find the best routes and show miracles of reaction to get to the top of the leaderboard!",
